    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルにならないか）\n（そう尋ねた俺に、芽衣は即答してくれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Do you want to be an idol?）\n（When I ask Mei this‚ her answer is immediate.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 130443.02743742753,
          "startTime": 133.44302743742753
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 6.866666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "いいよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": 10.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃たちになかったものが、芽衣にはある）\n（真面目過ぎる彼女らに必要な要素となる気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mei has something that Kotono and the others lack.）\n（Something necessary for an overly serious group of girls.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（しかしだ……問題は、どう琴乃たちに切り出すか）\n（いろいろ決めたことを怒られたばかりなのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The question is… how do I tell Kotono and the others?）\n（I’ve only just been told off by them for making a bunch of changes.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、琴乃ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ it’s me. Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.70000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃうわっ！\nなんだ…………麻奈か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaa!\nOh jeez… It’s just you‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.60666670004528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 32.04000003337861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "うふふ。そんなに怖いんだ\n琴乃のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pfft. Does Kotono scare you that much?\nMy little sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.46687063773474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ正直に言えばいいじゃない\nあと一人、増やしたいんだけど……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why not just be honest?\nJust tell her you wanna add another member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.718458012739845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "言ったらどうなると思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And what do you think would happen if I did that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.37714274326962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだねえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let me see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.55476184288663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（鬼の角が、俺の胸にブスブス刺さってきた）\n（感触はないが、針でつつかれている気持ちになる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her gaze is like demon horns piercing my chest.）\n（Despite no physical sensation‚ I feel I’m being poked by needles.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3214285095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ですよねえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.68809517621997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、そうでしょー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you expect?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.56154187917712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "この二つのグループにすればうまく行く！（キリッ）\nとか言ってわざわざグループ分けたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Everything’s gonna work out by dividing you into these two groups!”\nWasn’t that your reason for splitting them apart?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.10727879603707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "普通なら怒るよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they’ll be upset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.02123236425166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怒るよなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.48186731107478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "激おこだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Furious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.10164046056514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "激おこだよなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ furious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.65164041288142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何が激おこなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Furious about what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.98540460832362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こ、琴乃……\nおはよう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kotono?\nMorning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3315043347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.53150433468268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……なんでもない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no… It’s nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.30100542473242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 81.43433875806578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "何が足りないんですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it we’re missing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.13433875806578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.16767209139911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "他のアイドルのパフォーマンスを見て思ったんです\n今の自分達には何かが足りないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was watching videos of other idols performing.\nIt made me realize that we’re missing something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8343387581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "練習の後、みんなで自分達のダンスの録画を見て\n……それで思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After practice‚ we all re-watched a recording of our dancing.\nAnd I thought to myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.05708647241079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "上手下手以前に、何か決定的な差があるっていうか……\nオーラが違うっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are some fundamental differences beyond technique or skill.\nIt’s like the other groups give off a different aura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.423753139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "沙季さんや渚は、ステージに立つようになれば自然と\n箔とかオーラが付いてくるんじゃないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-san and Nagisa think that once we stand on stage‚\nwe’ll naturally develop that glamour or aura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.05708647241076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お姉ちゃんのデビュー前の映像を見たら\nやっぱり私達とは全然違っていて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I watch my sister’s videos before her debut‚\nshe’s completely different from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1237531391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、俺も思っていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I’ve been thinking the same thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.29041980574412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.42724512884898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
